Class LaunchPadServiceImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • lt.viko.eif.final_project.service.LaunchPadServiceImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LaunchPadService

    @Path(value="launchPads")
 @Consumes(value="application/json")
 @Produces(value="application/json")
public class LaunchPadServiceImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements LaunchPadService
    This class implements a RESTful web service, which allows the client to perform CRUD operations with a database through a launchPad DAO. This web service produces and consumes JSON documents.
    Author:
    Lukas Vanglikas
